item.title: gatotkaca
item.description: × GATOTKACA HD Wallpaper ❮ ❯ Gatotkaca 'The Iron Bone' was the son of Bima and Arimbi from Arcapada universe.Since his childhood, he's been a champion of Gods, fights vicious enemies of his homeland. Once lost and beaten near death,Gatotkaca arise as a mighty warrior from Pandava clan who possessed the supernatural power he got from the ultimate training inside the cauldron of heaven, Candradimuka.With his Antakusuma armor and Brajamusti-Brajadenta twin gauntlet, he can fly across the skies like lightning and hunt down his enemies, the furious Ashuras.
